https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e9%87%91%e7%b0%a1%2c132%2c20220418%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,金簡,132,20220418,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"金簡","JNO":"132","JDATE":"20220418","JTITLE":"洗錢防制法等"}